overview: CHIKARA crowns its first King of Trios champions! Max Boyer defends his Young Lions Cup. Hallowicked wrestles Matt Sydal, and Sara Del Rey fights Daizee Haze! In a special attraction bout, Mokujin Ken battles Mecha Mummy in a street fight! All this, plus the first annual Tag Team Gauntlet match.
title: Chikara: King of Trios 2007 (Night Three)
